ive Noise Cancellation enabled, using the case.*\nA MORE CAPABLE CASE— Keep track of AirPods Pro 2 with Precision Finding and a built-in speaker.* A lanyard loop helps keep your AirPods Pro 2 close. Charge with an Apple Watch or MagSafe Charger, USB-C Charge Cable, or Qi-certified charger.'
